frames.caption: A woman in a flowing white dress stands gracefully on a sailboat, holding onto the sail as the wind blows her hair. The sky is partly cloudy, and the boat is sailing on a vast body of water.
frames.description: The scene captures a serene moment on a sailboat, with a woman enjoying the breeze and the open water. The setting is tranquil, with a partly cloudy sky and gentle waves.

frames.caption: A woman in a white dress stands on a boat, looking at a large orca breaching the water nearby. The scene captures the dramatic moment as the whale emerges from the ocean against a backdrop of a partly cloudy sky.
frames.description: The image depicts a thrilling encounter between a person on a boat and a breaching orca in the ocean. The setting is a sunny day with scattered clouds, creating a vibrant and dynamic atmosphere.
